.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chrissie-hynde">克丽丝·海德 (Chrissie Hynde)</a>宣布即将在伦敦举办一场名为“<em>海德视觉 - 最近的绘画”</em>的艺术展。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/chrissie-hynde-people-die-of-loneliness-its-an-epidemic-2722497">克丽丝·海德（Chrissie Hynde）：“人们死于孤独——这是一种流行病”</a></strong></li></ul><p>周二（10 月 2 日），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-pretenders">伪装者</a>乐队主唱揭幕了她的最新画作展，共有 60 多幅作品可供参观。其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-eno">布莱恩·伊诺（Brian Eno）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-weller">保罗·韦勒（Paul Weller）</a>等“亲爱的朋友”的静物作品、自画像和画作。</p><p> <em>Hynde Sight</em>展览于 11 月 21 日在伦敦克伦威尔广场 4 号开幕，一直持续到 12 月 12 日，是与布罗德本特画廊 (Broadbent Gallery) 联合举办的，此前最近在萨奇画廊 (Saatchi Gallery) 举行的 2024 年英国艺术博览会上展出了海德 (Hynde) 的画作。 </p><figure id="attachment_3799614" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3799614" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3799614" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Afternoon-Poppies.jpg" alt="午后罂粟花" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Afternoon-Poppies.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Afternoon-Poppies-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Afternoon-Poppies-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Afternoon-Poppies-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Afternoon-Poppies-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Afternoon-Poppies-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3799614" class="wp-caption-text"> 《午后罂粟花》，60 x 90 厘米，作者：Chrissie Hynde。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>绘画已与这位“口袋里的黄铜”歌手更广泛的创意输出交织在一起，她的艺术作品为 2019 年的“Valve Bone Woe”提供了封面，并为 Vivienne Westwood 的 2021 年春夏系列提供了灵感。</p><p>在谈到即将举行的展览时，海德恩在一份声明中表示：“冥想练习已经变成了更实质性的东西，现在不能被忽视。</p><p> “就像一首等待被写的歌曲的歌词一样，这些画不断积累，想要被人看到。写遗嘱需要等待；需要采取行动——这些画必须得到处理。” </p><figure id="attachment_3799621" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3799621" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3799621" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Thursday-Evening-Bowl.jpg" alt="克丽丝·海德" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Thursday-Evening-Bowl.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Thursday-Evening-Bowl-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Thursday-Evening-Bowl-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Thursday-Evening-Bowl-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Thursday-Evening-Bowl-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Thursday-Evening-Bowl-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3799621" class="wp-caption-text">克丽丝·海德 (Chrissie Hynde) 的“周四晚间碗”。图片来源：新闻。</figcaption></figure><p><em>海德视觉 (Hynde Sight) – 近期绘画</em>展览可免费入场，开放时间为周二至周六上午 11 点至下午 7 点，周日上午 11 点至下午 4 点。</p><p>在其他地方，Hynde 将于 12 月与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Depeche-Mode">Depeche Mode</a>的 Dave Gahan 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Queens-Of-The-Stone-Age">Queens Of The Stone Age</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Josh-Homme">Josh Homme</a>一起担任<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-lanegan">Mark Lanegan</a>致敬演出的表演者。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/depeche-modes-dave-gahan-qotsas-josh-homme-chrissie-hynde-and-more-to-perform-at-mark-lanegan-tribute-show-in-london-3797013">这场名为“Mark Lanegan – 一场庆典”的演出将纪念这位已故歌手</a>兼词曲作家，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/mark-lanegan-has-died-aged-57-3167192">于 2022 年初去世，享年 57 岁</a>。</p><p>其他准备在演出门票现已售罄的演出中表演的音乐家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Primal-Scream">Primal Scream</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Bobby-Gillespie">Bobby Gillespie</a> 、Greg Dulli、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-Kills">The Kills</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Alison-Mosshart">Alison Mosshart</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Soulsavers">Soulsavers</a>等。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chrissie-hynde-reveals-why-the-pretenders-dont-play-arenas-clubs-and-theatres-are-better-for-the-audience-and-for-the-band-3779427">海德最近还解释了她和伪装者乐队不去竞技场演出的原因</a>，尽管他们可以，并表示他们更喜欢坚持在俱乐部和剧院演出，因为“对观众和乐队来说都更好”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chrissie-hynde-announces-london-art-show-hynde-sight-recent-paintings-3799603">Chrissie Hynde 宣布伦敦艺术展“Hynde Sight – 最近的绘画”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
